Name: Pixel-Warfare: Pro
About the game: Pixel-Warfare is BACK with better quality and improved gameplay. One of the most played games for Web Player and Webgl, with additional features that were not possible for browsers. The game includes: Multiplayer with up to 30 players Map editor to create your own custom maps...just click and your map will be ready and full with players 3 game modes: Deathmatch, Team Deathmatch and Zombies Full arsenal with weapons like snipers, shotguns, machineguns, granade launchers, pistols and more. Pixel-Warfare was created in 2014, and to this day continues to be updated with new features. Upcoming features: Map Editor: READY! Character Editor: IN PROGRESS... Weapons Editor: IN PROGRESS... Vehicles Editor: IN PROGRESS... We wish you... many many fun and successful shots.
